# Trend liniowy
# http://t-redactyl.io/blog/2016/05/creating-plots-in-r-using-ggplot2-part-11-linear-regression-plots.html

# http://r-statistics.co/Time-Series-Analysis-With-R.html
seq = c (1:nrow(dfN))
